<item>
            <title>[LU-14428] Convert tracefile to use ring_buffer  from linux</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14428</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Linux contains a ring_buffer which supports low-overhead appends for messages.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is similar to the trace log in tracefile.c, but with lower overhead.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Converting to use this removes a lot of code and reduces duplication for when we merge lustre upstream.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
